data.description: Updated home on over an acre in a lovely setting! This home has many features including: a large open floor plan, master bathroom with soaking tub and walk-in shower, ample storage in the kitchen, wood laminate flooring, and a cozy woodstove. Outside you will find a paved driveway, fully fenced property, two deck landings, new vinyl windows, & mature trees. Come enjoy this country property and make it your own! MF moved twice. Contact Banner Bank or Guild Mtg for financing. Seller & list agent are related.
